1
00:00:14,528 --> 00:00:17,984
...Until I return, I leave them in your care

2
00:00:22,720 --> 00:00:26,304
...The Knights of Favonius will always welcome you

3
00:00:34,677 --> 00:00:36,906
...Come on, to Mondstadt!

4
00:00:39,424 --> 00:00:41,088
Dear Grand Master...

5
00:00:41,856 --> 00:00:43,008
To Varka...

6
00:00:43,712 --> 00:00:44,992
To Varka...

7
00:00:46,272 --> 00:00:47,375
Family

8
00:00:47,375 --> 00:00:50,959
Lu-pi-cal

9
00:01:03,875 --> 00:01:04,884
...Poetry and letters

10
00:01:04,884 --> 00:01:08,475
Were humanity's earliest means of expressing their thoughts

11
00:01:11,300 --> 00:01:12,896
Make sure they all get delivered

12
00:01:12,946 --> 00:01:14,432
Outlander Who Caught the Wind!

13
00:01:36,211 --> 00:01:37,171
Grand Master!

14
00:01:37,171 --> 00:01:38,975
Grand Master...

15
00:01:38,975 --> 00:01:39,725
Master!

16
00:01:39,725 --> 00:01:40,475
Varka!

17
00:01:40,475 --> 00:01:41,300
Varka...

18
00:01:41,300 --> 00:01:42,825
Uncle Varka!

19
00:01:42,825 --> 00:01:44,339
Hey, Sir Writes-A-Lot!

20
00:01:44,659 --> 00:01:45,747
For Varka...

21
00:01:50,614 --> 00:01:55,253
The thoughts of others anchor you, reversing the assimilation...

22
00:01:56,299 --> 00:02:00,389
Using your connections, relying on outside help...

23
00:02:00,534 --> 00:02:02,768
This is not the way of a knight

24
00:02:03,700 --> 00:02:06,279
The Abyss can sustain me no longer

25
00:02:07,050 --> 00:02:08,155
But now

26
00:02:08,400 --> 00:02:11,667
Countless souls who died unjustly will emerge

27
00:02:11,667 --> 00:02:13,386
To prevent your return

28
00:02:14,150 --> 00:02:16,234
If you believe in your path

29
00:02:16,900 --> 00:02:18,714
Then grant them release

30
00:02:19,200 --> 00:02:21,636
Carve your way out through bloodshed...

31
00:02:22,355 --> 00:02:26,131
Varka, Mightiest Knight of Boreas

32
00:02:35,525 --> 00:02:39,101
This is how it ends... Throw the plan outta the window

33
00:02:39,925 --> 00:02:41,725
Fight my way to victory...

34
00:02:42,806 --> 00:02:43,556
Hah

35
00:02:46,575 --> 00:02:49,992
Well... That suits me just fine!

